  abstract = {This paper introduces a novel system for interactive modeling and
	designing of arbitrary BRDFs. The system is able to deal with BRDFs
	defined in a variety of forms, such as analytical models, measured
	data or data obtained by simulation. The system also allows designing
	BRDFs from scratch using a combination of different analytical lobes.
